Add customer testimonials to your site, with layout and styling customizations.


== Description ==
Add customer testimonials to your site, with layout and styling customizations.  Easy to use and fast to set up.  

Includes support for testimonial name, image, description, location, rating, and additional fields.  Set the section label, testimonials image size, order, and more.


== Frequently Asked Questions ==


== Installation == 
1. Upload the 'general-testimonials' folder in '/wp-content/plugins/' directory.
2. Activate the plugin in the Plugins menu in WordPress.
3. Use the shortcode [general_testimonials] where you want to output testimonials.


